ilm.com/films/query-2020|title=Query|website=[[Tribeca Film Festival]]|accessdate=March 6, 2020}}</ref> {{dagger|alt=Films that have not yet been released}}\n|\n| Sophie Kargman\n| Post-production; Short film\n|-\n| 2020\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#ffc;\" |''[[Dreamland (Nicholas Jarecki film)|Dreamland]]''{{dagger|alt=Films that have not yet been released}}\n| Jake Kahane\n| [[Nicholas Jarecki]]\n| Post-production\n|-\n| 2020\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#ffc;\" |''[[Death on the Nile (2020 film)|Death on the Nile]]''{{dagger|alt=Films that have not yet been released}}\n| Simon Doyle\n| [[Kenneth Branagh]]\n| Post-production\n|-\n| TBA\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#ffc;\" |''[[Rebecca (upcoming film)|Rebecca]]''{{dagger|alt=Films that have not yet been released}}\n|Maxim de Winter\n| Ben Wheatley\n| Post-production\n|-\n| TBA\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#ffc;\"| ''[[Next Goal Wins (upcoming film)|Next Goal Wins]]'' {{dagger|alt=Films that have not yet been released}}\n|\n| [[Taika Waititi]]\n| Post-production\n|}\n<!-- Per WP:NFF and WP:CRYSTAL, do not add films that are listed as \"pre-production\" -->\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 2005\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Arrested Development (TV series)|Arrested Development]]''\n| Student #2\n| Episode: \"[[The Immaculate Election]]\"\n|-\n| 2006\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Veronica Mars]]''\n| Kurt\n| Episode: \"[[Wichita Linebacker]]\"\n|-\n| 2007\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Desperate Housewives]]''\n| Barrett\n| Episode: \"[[Distant Past (Desperate Housewives)|Distant Past]]\"\n|-\n| 2009\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Reaper (TV series)|Reaper]]''\n| Morgan\n| 5 episodes\n|-\n| 2009\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Gossip Girl]]''\n| Gabriel Edwards\n| 4 episodes\n|-\n| 2012\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[The Simpsons]]''\n| Cameron and Tyler Winklevoss\n| Voices<br />Episode: \